scaledmarkets.dabl.analyzer

Class NameScope

  • java.lang.Object
    • scaledmarkets.dabl.analyzer.NameScope
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Annotation

    public class NameScope
extends java.lang.Object
implements Annotation
    All Axxx classes that define a lexical scope should be annotated with this. A NameScope contains a SymbolTable.

      • setSelfEntry

        public NameScopeEntry setSelfEntry(NameScopeEntry entry)
        Save reference to the entry that parent scope's symbol table has for this name scope. Thus, this is the symbol table entry for this scope's name. Note: a namespace does not have a self-entry, since the self entry would point outside the namespace (into the global symbol table), and we want the namespace model to be self-contained.
